  "title": "chore: upgrade AI SDK from v5 to v6 beta",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR upgrades the `ai` package from v5 (`^5.0.18`) to v6 beta (`6.0.0-beta.95`).\r\n\r\n**Breaking Changes**\r\n\r\nThe `addToolResult` callback in custom tool implementations has been renamed to `addToolOutput`.\r\n\r\nShould we keep exposing `addToolResult` and use `addToolOutput` internally?",
